{
  "title": "Delicate Garlicky Uruguayan Beef Stew",
  "description": "A light and flavorful Uruguayan dish featuring garlic and vinegar, cooked in a traditional ttukbaegi earthenware pot, suitable for a Buddhist temple meal.",
  "cuisine": "Uruguayan",
